<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تأليف<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>شمسِ الدِّينِ مُحَمَّدِ بنِ عبدِ القَوِيِّ الْمَرْدَاوِيِّ الْحَنْبَلِيِّ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#008000">(٦٣٠ هـ - ٦٩٩ هـ)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">اعْتَنَى بها وضَبَطَها:</span> مُحَمَّدُ بنُ ناصِرٍ العَجْمِيُّ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
